      <title>经济前景改善，南非商业信心保持稳定</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-12/south-africa-business-mood-steady-on-improved-economic-prospects</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非商业信心指数在去年底飙升至十年来最高水平，但 1 月份几乎没有变化，表明企业对该国的经济前景和联合政府的表现仍然持乐观态度。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-12/south-africa-business-mood-steady-on-improved-economic-prospects</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 12 Feb 2025 09:30:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
